These are runs that are in Tas3d/ on haise. They are meant to elucidate the processes that set the linear response on the shelf. Some of the analysis is from ProcessHaise and some is from AnalyzeTasmaniaSetupsNew, in particular the model forcing.

# OK, now we need to do for each:
moden = 1-1
L = dict()
R=dict()
Tot=dict()
In = dict()
for v in ['U','V','P']:
    U = Modes[v+'mAmp'][moden,:,:]*np.exp(1j*Modes[v+'mPha'][moden,:,:])
    xint = np.arange(Modes['x'][0],Modes['x'][-1],2.)
    xint = np.arange(40.,900,1.)
    m,n=np.shape(U)
    Uint = np.zeros((m,len(xint)),dtype='complex')
    for indy in range(m):
        Uint[indy,:]=np.interp(xint,Modes['x'],np.real(U[indy,:]))
        Uint[indy,:]+=np.interp(xint,Modes['x'],np.imag(U[indy,:]))*1j    
    # save
    Tot[v]=Uint
    #Fftu = np.fft.fft(Uint-np.mean(Uint,axis=1)[:,newaxis],axis=1)
    # taper ends
    if 0:
        N = 100
        H = np.hanning(N)
        taper = np.ones(len(Uint[0,:]))
        taper[:N/2]=H[:N/2]
        taper[-N/2:]=H[-N/2:]
        Uint=taper[newaxis,:]*Uint
    
    Fftu = np.fft.fft(Uint,axis=1)
    Ftemp = Fftu*1.
    n = len(xint)
    mid = np.int(np.floor(n/2))
    inl = np.arange(mid+1)
    Ftemp[:,inl]=0.
#    Ftemp[:,0]=np.mean(Uint,axis=1)
    R[v]= np.fft.ifft(Ftemp)
    Ftemp = Fftu*1.
    Ftemp[:,(mid+1):]=0.
#    Ftemp[:,0]=np.mean(Uint,axis=1)
    L[v] = np.fft.ifft(Ftemp)
    # get the incoming stuff
    U = InModes[v+'mAmp'][moden,:,:]*np.exp(1j*InModes[v+'mPha'][moden,:,:])
    m,n=np.shape(U)
    Uint = np.zeros((m,len(xint)),dtype='complex')
    for indy in range(m):
        Uint[indy,:]=np.interp(xint,Modes['x'],np.real(U[indy,:]))
        Uint[indy,:]+=np.interp(xint,Modes['x'],np.imag(U[indy,:]))*1j    
    # save
    In[v]=Uint

print L.keys()  
#left-going flux
def getF(U,V,P):
    F=0.5j*(np.real(V)*np.real(P)+np.imag(V)*np.imag(P))
    F+= 0.5*(np.real(U)*np.real(P)+np.imag(U)*np.imag(P))
    return F
if 1:
    
    Fl = getF(L['U'],L['V'],L['P'])
    Fr = getF(R['U'],R['V'],R['P'])
    Flpr = getF(R['U']+L['U'],R['V']+L['V'],R['P']+L['P'])
    Fc = getF(R['U'],R['V'],L['P'])
    Fc += getF(L['U'],L['V'],R['P'])
    
    Ftot = getF(Tot['U'],Tot['V'],Tot['P'])
    Fin = getF(In['U'],In['V'],In['P'])
    Fref = getF(Tot['U']-In['U'],Tot['V']-In['V'],Tot['P']-In['P'])
    Fcross = getF(In['U'],In['V'],Tot['P']-In['P'])
    Fcross+= getF(Tot['U']-In['U'],Tot['V']-In['V'],In['P'])
